data.description: Accepted Offer with Contingencies. Welcome home! This 2 bedroom 1 bath bungalow with an office space is move-in ready, great for your family or an investment. Updates include laminate flooring, interior paint, new carpet, and newer appliances. The shop has electricity and heat with lots of storage space. Enjoy afternoons out on the deck in the fully fenced backyard or pick delicious apples off the tree that will be ready this July!
